{"title":"Showcase README","type":"markdown","params":{"markdown":"# Overview

Welcome to your **Showcase Dashboard**! 
Here you'll find many example visualizations to get you started.

Please do not make any modifications to the **Showcase Dashboard**, as the system overwrites this dashboard periodically with new and exciting visualizations.  Be sure to check back from time to time to see whats new!

To modify, you can either utilize the Clone feature or create an entire new dashboard."},"aggs":[],"listeners":{}}
